{"tid":1212933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚瞓得好差，發咗個夢，快啲入嚟睇吓","createTime":"2019-06-12T23:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:55:59.000Z","uid":154702,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"100d64d0988eefa32020789e49d0b7619541bf11","tid":1212933,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:37:02.000Z","msg":"尋晚瞓得好差，發夢見到以下示威情節<br />\n從來未喺任何示威度見過<br />\n忍唔住畫圖同大家分享下<br />\n發夢見到自己唔響香港<br />\n場景好似係西方國家<br />\n唔記得夢中係因為乜嘢事而示威<br />\n好似同冇得飲酒有關<br />\n好奇怪，全部人都着住皮鞋<br />\n一邊係示威者，另一邊係冇靈魂嘅機械人部隊<br />\n<br />\n入正題：<br />\n夢見示威者用一條粗嘅麻繩<br />\n大概係小學生扯大纜用嗰啲<br />\n綁一個大嘅繩圈<br />\n埋牙同敵方對峙嘅時候<br />\n掉入去敵方防線之內<br />\n前方一發號施令<br />\n後方嘅示威者就多人用力向後拉<br />\n可能拉到盾牌，可能拉中敵方成員<br />\n前後兩者都可以增添示威者嘅裝備<br />\n<br />\n發夢仲見到有一兩個繩圈小隊圈中咗敵方成員<br />\n捉咗來做人質，可惜係機械人。<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持和平非暴力理性抗爭<br />\n<br />\n俯視圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4DBxMx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4DBxMx.png&h=b9bee975&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e9e70d80cf2c7e8d232928eae1338289078048e","tid":1212933,"uid":154702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:38:37.000Z","msg":"夢中仲見到有人同我講機械人冇配備短刀，所以用繩做武器特別有效"},{"pid":"a0979a1eec0de8852e50322dd307efaa697179f9","tid":1212933,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c5d58a7ed38f620daa83c8a20e78b55cac0554","tid":1212933,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b5e35e0cf0f77ef13969362a4297de6a8381f07","tid":1212933,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:51:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z3S-H_eajvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz3S-H_eajvI&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=4f0ad763\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z3